							</i></p>
							<p>
								Our patent-pending technology provides haptic feedback and control loading technology
								at a dramatically lower cost. The core technology is ideally suited for flight simulation,
								as well as remote operation applications in aerospace equipment, submersibles, vehicles
								and heavy machinery.
							</p>

							<div class='col-md-6 desc nospace'>
								<h3> Advantages </h3>
								<ul>
									<li> Cost Effective </li>
									<li> Low Latency - Smooth real-time response </li>
									<li> A single moving part increases reliability and lowers maintenance costs </li>
									<li> Precision feel reduces training consts </li>
